{"tid":896573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［你問我答］我在39000尺高空與292個西客鬥爭的日子","createTime":"2018-11-10T07:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T07:42:09.000Z","uid":73996,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"534fff712f242fa9368f70d928e03a5361731a49","tid":896573,"uid":73996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:06:58.000Z","msg":"其實男空姐同女空姐一樣，都係普通人一個。<br />\n<br />\n聽到有人講話咩空姐空少係飛雞飛鴨都係會唔開心。<br />\n聽到有人問你平時飛開邊度都係會覺得煩。<br />\n平時喺街聽到大陸話都係會覺得厭惡。<br />\n幫人hold住度門之後會唔小心同人講「多謝哂bye bye」。<br />\n見到人用尿袋會有衝動想同佢講「唔好意思啊飛機上面係唔可以用外置充電器㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n其實我地都可以好有禮貌。<br />\n但同時都可以好西。<br />\n<br />\n但係點都好，我哋都唔會喺你哋啲飛機餐入面加料。<br />\n點解？係責任啊DLGH.<br />\n無論啲客有幾西都好，落機嗰陣都會笑住同佢哋講句&rdquo;Thank you, see you next time&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\n仲有，餵飽你哋都係其次，你哋下次會唔會再搭我哋都唔重要。<br />\n重點係，你哋上得我地班機，我哋就有責任安全地送到你哋去目的地。<br />\n<br />\n咁多位師兄師姐有咩想問即管問，小弟24-hour standby."},{"pid":"fbfbf69fed9abb7306d3979f9c116e900b9149f6","tid":896573,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"認真，人工幾多？<br />\n做到幾多歲要轉行？"},{"pid":"32af564f3cd5c8b025eeffbc48551027f968e29c","tid":896573,"uid":30528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"我係一個會唔該前唔該後嘅飛容客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4349aa9f3860a061e027045d48c3ac1976665774","tid":896573,"uid":73996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbfbf69fed9abb7306d3979f9c116e900b9149f6","tid":896573,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"認真，人工幾多？<br />\n做到幾多歲要轉行？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"我地人工係分做3舊錢<br />\n<br />\n第一舊係老底<br />\n老底係跟番ranking同年資<br />\n<br />\n第二舊係flying hours, 之係鐘錢，由飛機推離停機坪嗰刻開始計（又好似係engine on嗰下開始計，唔太記得），直到飛機到埗熄engine.<br />\n<br />\n第三舊係allowance/其他雜項, 例如由我地duty start到飛機開始郁之前嘅鐘錢，飛到外地公司喺酒店出比我哋嘅錢，taxi claim, 同埋duty free commission等等。<br />\n<br />\n一個新入職FA人工（包括有上面提及嘅錢）一個月大約有18 - 22k<br />\n實際個range其實仲大，呢個只係約數。<br />\n<br />\n有人真係會做到退休，做到幾多歲要轉行呢啲真係好睇你人生追求嘅係咩。"},{"pid":"17f7e0a31ab1d86b814b3c4d66fa9eaa9103140f","tid":896573,"uid":73996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32af564f3cd5c8b025eeffbc48551027f968e29c","tid":896573,"uid":30528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"我係一個會唔該前唔該後嘅飛容客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"禮貌呢家野，睇你屋企點教：）"},{"pid":"f92b36bdcec46f9401961ee849c3f63ed855318f","tid":896573,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:39:42.000Z","msg":"有冇mark低晒d西客嘅名"},{"pid":"dd79c8cfb2a4aad91e2e50b01c20299875edb869","tid":896573,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"你是否基佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b828d467aa44691185168ae268a2e2d46ba5a5","tid":896573,"uid":73996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f92b36bdcec46f9401961ee849c3f63ed855318f","tid":896573,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:39:42.000Z","msg":"有冇mark低晒d西客嘅名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:59:31.000Z","msg":"點mark得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd767e07884e225dca7470f5e444a98a455a22eb","tid":896573,"uid":73996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd79c8cfb2a4aad91e2e50b01c20299875edb869","tid":896573,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"你是否基佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:59:58.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8cf8282b15ee4179b7f61e93b54efe9dea5df9","tid":896573,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd767e07884e225dca7470f5e444a98a455a